Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Tambongon Central Elementary and Barangay High School in the City of Davao to Alejandra L. Navarro Central Elementary and Barangay High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 667
An Act Changing the Name of the Tambongon Central Elementary and Barangay High School in the City of Davao to Alejandra L. Navarro Central Elementary and Barangay High School
Section 1. The name of the Tambongon Central Elementary and Barangay High School in the City of Davao is changed to Alejandra L. Navarro Central Elementary and Barangay High School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1avvphi1
Approved: March 7, 1984
